### Install the Kafkacat Utlility inthe CentOs 7 ###

Mandatory dependencies package to install git, gcc, librdkafka-devel ,librdkafka ,openssl-devel , cyrus-sasl etc.,

Step 01:

# git clone git@github.com:edenhill/kafkacat.git

Step 02:

Change the directory 

#cd kafkacat

Step 03 :

# sudo ./configure

Step 04 :

# sudo make
